## Customization

### Adding New Scenarios

Create a new file in `scenarios/` following this structure:

```yaml
# yaml-language-server: $schema=https://promptkit.altairalabs.ai/schemas/v1alpha1/scenario.json
apiVersion: promptkit.altairalabs.ai/v1alpha1
kind: Scenario
metadata:
  name: your-scenario

spec:
  id: your-scenario-id
  task_type: support
  description: "Your scenario description"
  
  turns:
    - role: user
      content: "Customer message"
      assertions:
        - type: content_not_empty
          params: {}
```

### Modifying the Support Agent

Edit `prompts/support-agent.yaml` to adjust:
- Tone and personality
- Specific guidelines
- Domain knowledge
- Escalation criteria

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all scenarios
promptarena run

# Run specific scenario
promptarena run --scenario basic-support

# Run with specific provider
promptarena run --provider openai-gpt4

# Generate HTML report
promptarena run --format html
```

